{"tid":711483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曝中國C919客機出現重大問題 已全面停飛","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T02:09:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":141,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"e814dedb2fe9e7ce7c229612211c27daf7b83ae1","tid":711483,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"中國研制的C919大飛機被曝已停飛以進行維修，整個過程計划耗時3個月時間。 6月15日，西方航空業網站&ldquo;ATW&rdquo;稱，中國商飛（COMAC）研制的C919原型機在測試中出現碳纤維复材升降舵剝落現象，已暫停試飛活動。 <br />\n<br />\n報道稱，另一位消息人士稱，C919原型機的油箱也正在進行改裝。 据稱，C919原型機自4月份以來未進行任何空中飛行測試活動，預計這一情況將持續到今年7月份。 <br />\n<br />\n今年3月24日，C919第二架原型機在上海機場完成初始檢查試飛。截至到目前，C919再無試飛活動。 報道認為，C919原型機出現問題會影響中國商飛的后續飛行測試"},{"pid":"773deed3dfb47a3a85a2fad8c0c585e103b22bc4","tid":711483,"uid":37735,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"搞D咩都搞到屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家日日吹噓新航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb00ac7229da47a7df7ef1eebb59125bbb2f44f","tid":711483,"uid":31237,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒事兒</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ef3b2bd5dfd8e9329feb754fc33bf5557774b83","tid":711483,"uid":108170,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"仲話佢地自己做個d飛機(c開頭) 係諗住同airbus Boeing 並列 ABC 咁樣 真係笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62221d1e1cc3253fbd1bc4af8f6570f0ebbc7bfd","tid":711483,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"咁雜種貿易戰打飛機既計劃點算?"},{"pid":"e731d728000bc989600e45f